{"tid":116584,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"講下你屋企人乞人憎既事例","createTime":"2017-02-11T13:47:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-14T16:50:34.000Z","uid":16181,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f81cd5cc675c02da67bfae5235b2d293ea1264ce","tid":116584,"uid":16181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T13:47:51.000Z","msg":"我阿哥好撚痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日哩係廁所一邊柯屎一邊打機<br />\n跟住再去浴缸開滿熱水浸番粒零鐘<br />\n一入去就霸兩三粒鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n岩岩佢又入左廁所了<br />\n我又要等兩粒鐘先有得沖涼<br />\n好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"378aeeb0ff8fb41f8160d62152279b9b3713648a","tid":116584,"uid":8569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T13:50:14.000Z","msg":"浸浴正"},{"pid":"f1118daeb3b57338a9a032267c4d0da8a5744609","tid":116584,"uid":16181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T13:51:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>浸浴正</blockquote><br />\n屌你喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔係大富大貴學咩人浸浴<br />\n又曬水，又曬時間，又霸撚住個廁所<br />\n<br />\n真係好撚嬲，但你又吹佢唔撚漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a09d1028660e9bcab08748c79c4eb41287eb3ad","tid":116584,"uid":80598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T13:53:11.000Z","msg":"自己要用就開哂燈，自己唔用就熄哂啲燈<br />\n屌你我重用撚緊電腦呀！！"},{"pid":"59dbc6182d8b2f4b733e3ef63c4808dca96ba5b8","tid":116584,"uid":16181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T13:54:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己要用就開哂燈，自己唔用就熄哂啲燈<br />\n屌你我重用撚緊電腦呀！！</blockquote><br />\n屌！開燈都算喇！<br />\n你地入房訓覺之前可唔可以熄燈呀？<br />\n成撚日個廳明明無人，又開撚完燈，之後走入房<br />\n<br />\n點解次撚次都要我熄？！！！！"},{"pid":"c1b00f3ca5d2467f0a2ccaf046c2f2e5944c7eb9","tid":116584,"uid":80598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T13:59:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自己要用就開哂燈，自己唔用就熄哂啲燈<br />\n屌你我重用撚緊電腦呀！！</blockquote><br />\n屌！開燈都算喇！<br />\n你地入房訓覺之前可唔可以熄燈呀？<br />\n成撚日個廳明明無人，又開撚完燈，之後走入房<br />\n<br />\n點解次撚次都要我熄？！！！！</blockquote><br />\n我同你個情況啱啱好相反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6894e0db584a5983316c2fad79f2a0825855827","tid":116584,"uid":55789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T14:12:50.000Z","msg":"屙屎永遠唔鎖門 我一開門就急住 咁拍返埋對門次次想去廁所見到著住燈都心戰緊入面究竟有無人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df946c940a8566f6e9784518b86c5e6024b99e4a","tid":116584,"uid":16181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T14:50:24.000Z","msg":"屌！沖撚完未呀？<br />\n又入去浸浴，溫泉呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c22821bf3b5261f6e7ff98d95e26b615ed218d","tid":116584,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T14:56:15.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪同家姐時辰八字唔夾 定還是佢捕撚住我 無論我幾點去廁所佢就會敲門話肚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試過朝早八點 晏就四點 零晨三點佢都會敲門去廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n十次有八次都係咁 去到一半就話要去 我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39dade7917f3864b85d4c4d22c8ea3ee00b04e13","tid":116584,"uid":41238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T14:58:41.000Z","msg":"細佬成日食完啲空盒就放返原位扮冇食到，好多次我係櫃或者雪櫃拎先發現入面已經係空既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌佢 唔明佢咩思維，以為冇人知佢食左？"},{"pid":"e43d6ef824504ab5385f1cfd2ea4599e95d8ca22","tid":116584,"uid":18547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T14:58:48.000Z","msg":"自己一唔洗用某個電器就熄撚左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日話慳電慳電"},{"pid":"43dc9b5fd9c8c142662f516f7c7678012fe24b73","tid":116584,"uid":16181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T15:01:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知係咪同家姐時辰八字唔夾 定還是佢捕撚住我 無論我幾點去廁所佢就會敲門話肚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試過朝早八點 晏就四點 零晨三點佢都會敲門去廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n十次有八次都係咁 去到一半就話要去 我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> I know that feel！<br />\n廁所呢d野真係唔爭就會唔想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你老味沖撚完未呀仆街仔？"},{"pid":"f18fe5a02735bac8ce0afa184d3f61576d1493e2","tid":116584,"uid":16181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T15:01:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細佬成日食完啲空盒就放返原位扮冇食到，好多次我係櫃或者雪櫃拎先發現入面已經係空既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌佢 唔明佢咩思維，以為冇人知佢食左？</blockquote><br />\n可能佢細個姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你細佬幾過癮"},{"pid":"7087d328afb4862da1146e5c7a9801fdfba93839","tid":116584,"uid":80598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T15:02:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細佬成日食完啲空盒就放返原位扮冇食到，好多次我係櫃或者雪櫃拎先發現入面已經係空既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌佢 唔明佢咩思維，以為冇人知佢食左？</blockquote><br />\n可能佢細個姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你細佬幾過癮</blockquote><br />\n不如同佢講吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實掉咗佢咪重快過放返原位，佢究竟諗緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d52e2690fb4d16