/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出左<br />\n<br />\n岩岩沖完我即刻仆入去沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而加終於可以訓覺覺豬"},{"pid":"fc5717ed208bc15e8e52dd3af1c742972ea661ed","tid":116584,"uid":24386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T16:05:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"270a504c68be4486c1a7a00889e1d356f04cb6c5","tid":116584,"uid":41238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T17:01:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>細佬成日食完啲空盒就放返原位扮冇食到，好多次我係櫃或者雪櫃拎先發現入面已經係空既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌佢 唔明佢咩思維，以為冇人知佢食左？</blockquote><br />\n可能佢細個姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你細佬幾過癮</blockquote><br />\n不如同佢講吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實掉咗佢咪重快過放返原位，佢究竟諗緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我細佬都唔細傢啦 19歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我有講過 次次見到都捉佢話一餐 我話你食左咪食左囉 裝個垃圾放返入雪櫃做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但佢都繼續係咁，上次先放左個空雪糕盒係雪櫃"},{"pid":"774badca7ffb686288ddccadd5dc07c394254d29","tid":116584,"uid":80598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T17:03:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>細佬成日食完啲空盒就放返原位扮冇食到，好多次我係櫃或者雪櫃拎先發現入面已經係空既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌佢 唔明佢咩思維，以為冇人知佢食左？</blockquote><br />\n可能佢細個姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你細佬幾過癮</blockquote><br />\n不如同佢講吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實掉咗佢咪重快過放返原位，佢究竟諗緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我細佬都唔細傢啦 19歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我有講過 次次見到都捉佢話一餐 我話你食左咪食左囉 裝個垃圾放返入雪櫃做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但佢都繼續係咁，上次先放左個空雪糕盒係雪櫃</blockquote><br />\n咁黐線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全諗唔明點解要咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8f0874a255c140dc6d9a54ee88ba059b6d5654","tid":116584,"uid":31368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T21:01:31.000Z","msg":"室內食煙，冇手尾，近來有次明明垃圾桶伸手都唔使就到都寧願放垃圾入杯度，唔沖涼洗頭，好撚臭"},{"pid":"1cf271113d15a9011d0bd78a3e2924956bebf687","tid":116584,"uid":80598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T03:42:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>室內食煙，冇手尾，近來有次明明垃圾桶伸手都唔使就到都寧願放垃圾入杯度，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔沖涼洗頭</strong></span>，好撚臭</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好嘔心"},{"pid":"3b4f9ea39451a106b78f500eaf2e7380fbac1eb5","tid":116584,"uid":31368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T07:59:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>室內食煙，冇手尾，近來有次明明垃圾桶伸手都唔使就到都寧願放垃圾入杯度，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔沖涼洗頭</strong></span>，好撚臭</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好嘔心</blockquote><br />\n所以我好憎佢仲訓呀媽張床"},{"pid":"be066432adc8cf0d3e329f2220d6bd8d2642a840","tid":116584,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T19:41:13.000Z","msg":"老人家唔講衛生 詳情唔想講 會嘔"}]}